14/03/2011
PODGORICA, Montenegro -- People in Montenegro will not be obliged to declare their ethnicity, religious affiliation or mother tongue during the upcoming population census, representatives of the statistical office said on Sunday (March 13th).
The census will be held from April 1st to 15th, with first final results published in January 2012.
The last official headcount was conducted in 2003.
(RTCG, RTS - 13/03/11)
